data.description: This charming Craftsman home boasts original wood ceilings and floors, preserving the timeless elegance of its architectural heritage. The updated kitchen seamlessly blends modern convenience with classic charm. Located in the heart of this waterfront town it is a quick stroll to the Windjammer Beach Park, vibrant festivals, eclectic shopping destinations, and a diverse array of restaurants. Outside, a tranquil garden space awaits, providing a retreat for relaxation and enjoying the beauty of nature. The presence of a greenhouse allows for year-round gardening, while a workshop space caters to those with a penchant for DIY projects or creative endeavors. This Craftsman gem offers a delightful lifestyle in a picturesque setting.
